# Deployment & Tenancy

One Docker deploy per buyer: `customers/{slug}/config.yaml` + `.env` (`POSTGRE_URL`, secrets).

Config includes **`locale`** (`zh-TW` default for Taiwan merchants) — fixed at onboarding, not changeable in app.

|          | Independent deploy | SaaS (defer)            |
| -------- | ------------------ | ----------------------- |
| DB       | PG per buyer       | shared PG + `tenant_id` |
| Language | `locale` in YAML   | per-tenant setting      |

**Delivery:** discovery → config (modules + locale) → compose deploy → expand via config.

Features + locale in config; secrets in `.env`.
